    Method and Description

    fmpp.models.TemplateModelUtils.dieWithMissingParam(String)
    Use throw TemplateModelUtils.newMissingParamException(String).
    fmpp.models.TemplateModelUtils.dieWithParamsNotAllowed()
    Use throw TemplateModelUtils.newNoParamsAllowedException().
    fmpp.models.TemplateModelUtils.dieWithUnknownParam(String)
    Use throw TemplateModelUtils.newUnsupportedParamException(String).
    fmpp.Engine.getFreeMarkerVersionNumber()
    Use Engine.getFreeMarkerVersion() instead. If you have need a String, it has a proper Version.toString().
    fmpp.Engine.getVersionNumber()
    Use Engine.getVersion() instead. If you have need a String, it has a proper Version.toString().

    Use Engine.addLocalDataBuilder(int, String, LocalDataBuilder) instead
